the company also said it planned to hire some 55 000 seasonal workers for the holidays .
at the same time last year , FedEx reported that hiring 50,000 temporary workers for the holidays .
its shares slipped by about 2.5 per cent at the preliminary bidding for 45 minutes before the exchange opened on Wednesday .
