however , the boom of online shopping has dramatically improved the results in the FedEx Ground .
in the last quarter , revenue from land transportation grew by 29 % , but operating income remained unchanged due to higher costs for large departures and self-insurance .
the express transport division has received higher revenue because of higher base rates , while in the freight sector , income has fallen because of increased labor costs .
